title: Crime Alert 10.03.18

description:
Some deployed servicemen will be allowed to vote in the midterm elections via app. Florida mom charged after her baby died, forgotten in a hot car. Boyfriend of woman who cuts baby from a friend's womb found not guilty of conspiring to commit murder.
